title: Grateful Dead Live at Riverport Amphitheatre on 1994-07-26
description:
Set 1

Soundcheck:

Drummers join Vince Bob & Phil,	Vince little keyboard jam, Mickey on the beam w/ Phil, A Day In The Life, A Day In The Life, Childhood’s End, Childhood’s End, Piano Ragtime Noodle Jam

Set 2

Jack Straw, Friend Of The Devil, Little Red Rooster, Lazy River Road, Queen Jane Approximately*, Tennessee Jed, Childhood's End, Easy Answers-> Deal

Set 3

China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider, Victim Or The Crime-> Samba In The Rain, Ship of Fools, Estimated Prophet-> Drums-> Space-> The Wheel-> Attics Of My Life-> Sugar Magnolia, E: I Fought the Law

* Weir on acoustic

reviews.review_text: Mr. Darby does it again! An excellent recording of a very good show. 18 years later, and I'm sitting here blown away by the band and the technology that allows me this gift.
